{ My Bedroom}
{My Bedroom}is always untidy and I hate tidying it up. My bedroom has a long white{wardrobe}in which I put my clothes. I have a{cupboard}with a set of drawers where I keep my{toys}and the things that I cannot hang up. In my bedroom I have a{bed}that folds into a sofa for two. I have got a pink carpet and a brown bed. At the side, on a wall I have got a{Sindy House with two dolls in it. I do a lot of moving about with the things in the rooms. I like to read{books}and I have a lot of them. I spend a lot of time in my bedroom. Angela Marney (Age 8)
Angela Marney, Marcus Burrows and Lucy Tunney are from St Bede's Primary Schhol, Redbridge.
